PPBUS_G3H is 8.59v
PP3V3_S5 IS 3.3V 
PPVRTC IS 3.42V 
ALL_SYS_PWRGD IS 0V 
PP5V_S4RS3 IS 0V..
does this board needs battery to power on ?

No, it should turn on when charger is plugged in.
Be aware, it restarts 3 times, like its bigger sister 3437.

Any history available?
Tried SMC bypass?

Check PM_BATLOW_L, PM_DSW_PWRGD, PCH_DSWVRMEN, SMC_ADAPTER_EN, PM_RSMRST_L, PM_SLP_SUS_L and the 4 PCH's RTC signals.
